            <p class="text-[#0d4d3e] font-lato font-light leading-relaxed"><strong>Which structure is best for you?</strong> It depends on your business structure, GST registration status, cash flow preferences, and how you want to claim tax deductions. Nik Finance helps you compare not just rates but structures — so you choose the option that delivers the best overall outcome for your business. We always recommend consulting your accountant before committing to a finance structure.</p>
