            <p class="text-gray-700 font-lato font-light leading-relaxed">Yes. While the best rates are reserved for borrowers with clean credit, there are specialist lenders who provide equipment finance for businesses with impaired credit — including paid defaults, discharged bankruptcies, and other credit events. Rates will be higher (typically 10–18% p.a.) and a deposit may be required. Having strong current business cash flow and the equipment as security works in your favour.</p>
